8 An Act relating to professions and occupations;
amending 59 O.S. 2021, Sections 1000.20, 1000.21,
9 1000.23 and 1000.25, which relate to the Oklahoma
Uniform Building Code Commission Act; updating
10 internal citations; modifying membership and
appointment requirements; modifying powers and duties
11 of the Commission to include to continuing education
requirements; providing for the assessment of certain
12 fee; directing the deposit of fee into certain fund;
establishing work development process to increase
13 code official development; providing for the
promulgation of certain rules; updating reference to
14 certain permit allowing for the electronic submission
of collections report; and providing an effective
15 date.
16
17 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
18 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 59 O.S. 2021, Section 1000.20, is
19 amended to read as follows:
20 Section 1000.20. Sections 1000.20 through 1000.29 1000.30 of
21 this title shall be known and may be cited as the "Oklahoma Uniform
22 Building Code Commission Act".
23 SECTION 2. AMENDATORY 59 O.S. 2021, Section 1000.21, is
24 amended to read as follows:
